name: DiamondHold
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en: DiamondHold is a BEP-20 token that builds upon the popular frictionless yield mechanic that is currently very popular on the Binance Smart Chain. It introduces the concept of a wallet ranking system, where any wallet that owns $DHOLD is ranked based on the time it has held these tokens (from first purchase date Starting at Tier 1 and eventually maturing into a Tier 4 wallet, these ranks determine the amount of tax a wallet incurs on a trade, and the reflection rewards gained by that wallet.
